{"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"